context: Automator AI stands as a no-code automation tool, empowering users to formulate test prompts in plain English. The tool's functionality lies in its adept utilization of natural language processing and automation technology, seamlessly converting these plain English test prompts into automated test scripts. This streamlined process is followed by the execution of these scripts, with the results presented in a clear format featuring pass/fail icons. The underlying principle of Automator AI revolves around automating the automation testing process, providing users with an intuitive and efficient means of conducting tests.
